Fix MessageOriginChat::getChat() returning null.

The entity registers sub-entity under key "sender_chat" but the PHPDoc
(and Longman's DB::insertMessageRequest) expects getChat() to return the
sender chat. Provide an explicit getChat() alias.

--- a/src/Entities/MessageOrigin/MessageOriginChat.php
+++ b/src/Entities/MessageOrigin/MessageOriginChat.php
@@ -22,4 +22,9 @@ class MessageOriginChat extends Entity implements MessageOrigin
             'sender_chat' => Chat::class,
         ];
     }
+
+    public function getChat(): ?Chat
+    {
+        return $this->getSenderChat();
+    }
 }
